reak: break-all\" size=\"3\"><b style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; color: red; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">3504</font></span></b><b style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; word-break: break-all\">地埋式旋转喷头</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">：该系列喷头为小射程旋转式</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">,</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">适用于公园、游乐场、校园、工矿企业、街道等中小面积草坪、花卉的喷灌。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">主要特点</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">材料为</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-br