rial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">融全圆和扇形喷洒为一体，顶部扇形调节，操作简单，更换喷嘴方便，射程调节螺钉可减小</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">35%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">射程。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">技术性能</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">工作压力：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">0.17-0.38Mpa<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">流量：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">0.12-1.04m3/h</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">射程：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">4.6-10.7m<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">扇形角度调节范围：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">40&deg;-360&deg;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>3504</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">接口：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">G1/2&rdquo;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">内螺纹</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>∙</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; word-break: break-all\">升降高度：</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" face=\"Times New Roman\">102mm</font></span></font></p>\r\n</span></span>'),(24,'<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; border-collapse: separate; font: medium Verdana, Arial; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"Apple-style-span\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12px\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">来源：http://www.xllj.cn/news/JCPBJDDJCFF.html<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n检测平台所属类别： 铸铁平板平台系列<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n的用途：主要用于精密工件的检测。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n检测平台的别称： 检测平台、精密检测平台、铸铁检测平台、钳工检测平台<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n检测平台简介： 检测平台的材料：HT200-300；检测平台的硬度：HB170-240；检测平台的精度：0-3级；检测平台执行标准：JB/T7974-1999.检测平台主要用于铆焊，焊接，检验、试验，装配，动力机械试验等。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n检测平台尺寸： 检测平台整体规格4000mm*8000mm以下各种规格,大于此规格可以拼接使用!<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n<b style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">检测平板</b></span></span>'),(25,'<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; border-collapse: separate; font: medium Verdana, Arial; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"Apple-style-span\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12px\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">2011年法兰克福家用纺织品展 欧意达国际展览（北京）有限公司-提供10#馆、6.3#馆、 2011年法兰克福家纺展 Heimtextil2011&nbsp; 张 璐&nbsp; 010-65202355摊位保证 市场最低价 2011年德国家纺展张 璐&nbsp; 010-6520235 2011年全球最专业的家纺展 摊位保证 欧意达国际展览北京有限公司张 璐&nbsp; 010-6520235 2010年土耳其家纺展 2010年美国家纺展 英国家纺展 俄罗斯家纺展 迪拜家纺展 迪拜家纺展 日本家纺展 南非家用纺织品展览 哈萨克斯家纺展 中国区总代&nbsp; 张 璐&nbsp; 010-65202355市场最低价 德国国际家纺展会 国际家纺展会 Heimtextil Frankfurt2011 全球家纺展 世界第一家纺展 全球展览网 家纺展览网 欧洲家纺展 欧洲家纺展览网 世界家纺展 世界规模最大家纺展 针对性最强家纺展 成交量最高家纺展<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\"><strong style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">2011年德国法兰克福国际家用纺织品展览会</strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(255,153,0); word-break: break-all\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\"><strong style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\">（保展位）</strong></span></span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n06、07、08、09、2010年我司连续成功出团，欢迎登陆我司网站观看摊位照片及团队合影！<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n2010年摊位面积1000多平米，摊位分布在10号馆和6号馆,组成了192人的参展团队，成为此次展会中国组展单位最大的团队。如有考虑2011年该展会，请尽快预定！！欢 迎 参 观 及 考 察。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n展会时间：2011年1月12-15日&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n展会地点： 法兰克福展览中心&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n主办单位：法兰克福展览公司&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n展会介绍： &ldquo;Heimtextil&rdquo; - 法兰克福国际家用及室内纺织品展览会 -- 是法兰克福最为成功的展览会品牌之一，同时也是该领域规模最大、国际性最强的展会。如今，&ldquo;Heimtextil&rdquo;仍在不断发展壮大，力保业界同类展会领头羊的地位。&ldquo;Heimtextil&rdquo;是广大来自设计、创意、制造领域的高质量展商梦寐以求的展示良机，也是整个业界发布家具布艺、室内装潢新品、最新潮流和设计的理想平台。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n展品分类：装饰布、 窗门及附件（纺织类）、精美刺绣、纤维制品、纱线、布料、印染、家纺辅料、家具装饰布、家具皮革、墙纸及墙面涂料、墙纸附件、垫子、地毯、毛毯、纬线、床架、床板、床垫、床垫套、蒲团、水床、毯子和枕头、被单和枕套 、餐布、餐桌装饰品、厨房用纺织品、绒布制品、毛巾、浴帘、浴垫、地毯、沐浴用品等。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n注：亚洲馆10号馆的主要展品：浴室纺织品（毛巾、浴巾、沙滩巾、浴袍等）；床上纺织品（被子、枕头、四件套、床垫等），厨房纺织品（围裙、手套等），餐桌纺织品（桌布、台布等）。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n亚洲馆6号馆的主要展品：窗帘、窗纱、沙发布、家具布、床单布等各种家纺面料、毛毯、地毯、靠垫、家纺辅料、窗帘杆、墙纸、墙纸附件等；非所在展馆的展品占整个展品的比例不得超过30%。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n欢迎不参展的企业随团考察！费用：人员费 + 报名费。<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n&nbsp;<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n组展单位：欧意达国际展览（北京）有限公司<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n地址：北京市朝阳区东四环中路39号华业国际中心B座219室&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n直拨：010-65202355/65202377<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n传真：010-85592080&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\nE-mail：ouyida258@sina.com<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\nMSN: zl_oyd@live.cn<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; word-break: break-all\" />\r\n联系人：张 璐</p>\r\n</span></span>');

